message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $110. I think it's a great deal for you considering its value.
Hi Alice, thanks for the offer. I'm interested, but $110 is a bit high for me. I'm willing to pay $95 for the product.  Let me know what you think.
Hi Bob, thanks for your offer. I appreciate your interest. I can go down to $100, but I can't go any lower than that.  It's still a great deal!
